Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.00,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ešte kúsok!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Počkajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.12,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan, pozri sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.22,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,To sú oni.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.45,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Čo spravíme?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:10.16,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Ak pôjdeme ďalej, chytia nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.59,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Môžeme si prebojovať únikovú cestu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:13.61,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Som za.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.22,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Ak to vyjde, budeme mať auto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.28,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Ja môžem šoférovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.73,Rika,,0,0,0,,Ty máš vodičský preukaz?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.52,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Toto je núdzový prípad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.59,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Nesmieš ľpieť na maličkostiach!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.58,Satoko,,0,0,0,,To je výborný nápad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.54,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Dobre, rozhodnuté...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.65,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ideme na to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To je ona!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Chyťte ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:48.98,Rena,,0,0,0,,Jeden dole!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.41,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Musíš si kryť chrbát.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.22,Rena,,0,0,0,,To nechávam na teba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.59,Rena,,0,0,0,,Vďaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.39,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nezabila si ho, že nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.06,Rena,,0,0,0,,Neboj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:02.44,Rena,,0,0,0,,Sekám tupou stranou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Prekliaty pangharti...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:14.50,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Bola by som radšej, keby si ma nepodceňoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.38,MionShion,,0,0,0,,To je ovocie našich klubových hier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.33,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Myslím že to bol posledný.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.70,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,To bolo ľahké.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:31.68,Rena,,0,0,0,,To pretože sme bojovali spoločne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:34.63,Rena,,0,0,0,,Boli sme šiesti proti šiestim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.85,Rena,,0,0,0,,Určite by sme to dokázali
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.55,Rena,,0,0,0,,keby tu niekto z nás chýbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:39.84,Rika,,0,0,0,,Presne tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.23,Rika,,0,0,0,,Ak budeme bojovať spolu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.92,Rika,,0,0,0,,určite sa nám podarí poraziť osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.10,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Zdá sa že sú to profíci.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.75,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Myslíš že sa tí prvý už prebrali?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:57.80,MionShion,,0,0,0,,To sú všetci?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.39,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Nás je viac.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:02.05,Rika,,0,0,0,,Keď pôjdeme spolu, nemusíme sa báť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:03.52,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hanyuu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:06.78,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Už si sa vzdala, však? Ako vždy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:12.60,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stoj tu a pozeraj sa, čo dokážeme, keď bojujeme spoločne.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.66,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ideme!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:23.42,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Teraz zmeníme... náš osud!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.62,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.68,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Takano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:44.88,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:45.91,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Nezomieraj!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:52.91,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,P-prepáčte...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.41,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Asi budem musieť ustúpiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:57.90,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,No tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.76,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Bežte preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:00.75,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.84,MionShion,,0,0,0,,To nemôže byť pravda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:05.49,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeš len tak zomrieť!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.67,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Čože...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:14.95,Rena,,0,0,0,,No tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.43,Rena,,0,0,0,,Ideme!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:19.58,Rena,,0,0,0,,Teraz hlavne musíme prežiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:23.26,Rena,,0,0,0,,Keiichi určite nechce, aby sme tu ostali!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.46,Rena,,0,0,0,,Utekajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.78,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Musíte prežiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.52,Rena,,0,0,0,,Je ich stále viac a viac!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.56,Rena,,0,0,0,,Bežte!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:52.57,Rena,,0,0,0,,Mii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.30,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Ja ich odlákam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.39,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Odlákam ich
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.74,MionShion,,0,0,0,,a vy zatiaľ utečte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.02,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Mion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.19,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Nemáme čas hádať sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.64,MionShion,,0,0,0,,A ty sa musíš postarať o Satoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:07.19,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Rena!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:08.86,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Daj za mňa pozor na Riku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:10.55,Rena,,0,0,0,,Poďme, Rika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.89,Rika,,0,0,0,,M-Mii...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.08,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Mii!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:20.74,Rena,,0,0,0,,Len na chvíľku, dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.63,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Ja viem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.43,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Tá hlupaňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.63,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Prečo sa zrovna teraz musí hrať na hrdinu..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.41,Rena,,0,0,0,,Kto je tam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.40,Rena,,0,0,0,,Mii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.00,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Onee! Si v poria-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:38.02,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Mion... san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ona je už mŕtva.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:46.94,Rena,,0,0,0,,Shii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.55,Rena,,0,0,0,,Postaraj sa o ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.61,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Rena-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:50.62,Rena,,0,0,0,,Rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:58.64,Rena,,0,0,0,,Takže Vy stojíte za celou Hinamizawskou sériou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:01.64,Rena,,0,0,0,,Myslíte si o sebe, že ste Oyashirova zástupkyňa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nie, zástupkyňa nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ja sama som strojcom kliatby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kliatba ktorá padne na vašu dedinu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,je moja kliatba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A až sa tak stane,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,ja prekročím ľudskosť
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a stanem sa bohom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stanem sa Oyashirom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:22.72,Rena,,0,0,0,,Myslím že to je nemožné.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.72,Rena,,0,0,0,,Je jedno čo urobíte,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:27.05,Rena,,0,0,0,,bohom sa stať nemôžete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.91,Rena,,0,0,0,,Nemôžete sa stať Oyashirom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Môžem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stanem sa ním ešte dnes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.77,Rena,,0,0,0,,Vravím Vám že je to nemožné.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.85,Rena,,0,0,0,,Pretože Oyashiro-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.35,Rena,,0,0,0,,...už existuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:48.91,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Rena...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.49,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Už dosť...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.51,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Ja už to nevydržím!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.65,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Proste ma zabite...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.83,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Tak ma už zabite!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.84,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Satoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.00,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Už nikdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.68,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Takto už nikdy nehovor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.69,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Shion-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.46,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Musíš sa snažiť, aj keby ti to malo zachrániť len jedinú minútu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.75,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Musíš!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.31,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Ochránim ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.92,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Aj za Satoshiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:15.16,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Nii-nii...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A teraz...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,S kým by som mala začať?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.65,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Nezabíjajte Satoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:35.86,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Prosím Vás!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:38.33,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Ak ma chcete zabiť, zabite ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.62,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Ale prosím, neubližujte Satoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaujímaví návrh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Prosila ma o to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Čo myslíš, Satoko-chan, čo by som mala spraviť teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:15:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Čo by si povedala na taký malí kvíz?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brokolica alebo karfiol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Čo z toho je zelené?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.14,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Karfi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.08,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Brokolica.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Výborne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:25.24,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,A teraz zabiješ mňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Samozrejme.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mŕtve telo "kráľovnej" je pre našu operáciu kľúčové.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Si tak ďaleko od Tokia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ktoré ťa zneužívalo vo svojej hanebnej hre...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ale ty v skutočnosti
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ukončíš všetky legendy o dedine "Onigafuchi".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:46.18,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Možno by si si to mala ešte premyslieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dobrú noc...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...Rika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:53.12,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Počkajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ale, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chceš prosiť o svoj život?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:56.81,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.68,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Ale ak ma chcete zabiť,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.14,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,spravte to bez toho, aby ste ma uspali.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Čo to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nechceš zomrieť bez bolesti?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Vieš, my ti budeme trhať vnútornosti. A to bolí.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.06,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Aspoň na to nezabudnem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:17.29,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Chcem mať meno toho, kto mi rozpára brucho, naveky vpálené do duše.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.63,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Pretože len tak si ho zapamätám
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:24.13,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,až sa znovu stretneme!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:31.68,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Rika...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:32.89,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Opäť...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:34.66,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Opäť sa nám to nepodarilo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.83,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}To nevadí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:40.47,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bojovali sme zo všetkých síl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.05,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}A boli sme blízko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.45,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Rika...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.74,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale ja sa nevzdám.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:50.62,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aj kedy sa tieto spomienky stratili...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:54.17,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aj keby mala ďalšia Hinamizawa skončiť tragédiou...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:58.15,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Budem bojovať a raz sa mi to určite podarí!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.20,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale tentokrát...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.88,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}...nezabudnem...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.46,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}...na svoju smrť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.80,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Ani ja na ňu nezabudnem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.21,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Aj keby si zabudla, Rika,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:21.58,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,ja ti ju pripomeniem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.54,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Aj ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:27.37,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Aj ja chcem zažiť šťastnú budúcnosť s ostatnými!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:35.98,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Priatelia...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.73,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Je to škoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.28,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Chýbal nám už len kúsok a mohli sme poraziť osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:48.15,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Ale každý z vás dal do boja svoje srdce a bojovali zo všetkých síl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:50.06,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Videla som to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.53,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Všetko som to videla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.51,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:54.93,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,To nestačilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:58.25,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ak by bola naša túžba poraziť osud len o trochu silnejšia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.17,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Všetci sme verili že to dokážeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:04.00,MionShion,,0,0,0,,A chýbal nám len malí kúsok.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.91,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Je mi to ľúto, Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.52,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Nemohla som ťa zachrániť...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.38,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.57,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}To je v poriadku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:14.89,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ďakujem vám všetkým.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:16.60,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Z hĺbky srdca vám ďakujem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.18,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vzdávam sa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:37.15,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aj keď sme spojili všetky naše sily, nedokázali sme spraviť zázrak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.51,Rena,,0,0,0,,Mýliš sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:43.64,Rena,,0,0,0,,Ja viem prečo sa ten zázrak nestal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:47.92,Rena,,0,0,0,,Aj {\i1}ty{\i0} si naozaj verila že sa stane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.34,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Hauauau...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.13,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Ja nič nedokážem...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.07,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Som úplne zbytočná.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:56.13,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Môžem sa len prizerať.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:58.54,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,To že budem veriť-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:00.04,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,-dokáže zázrak privolať.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:02.63,MionShion,,0,0,0,,To je pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:05.25,MionShion,,0,0,0,,Ak by si sa pridala k nám
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:06.98,MionShion,,0,0,0,,určite by sme vyhrali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:11.27,Rena,,0,0,0,,Musíš len nájsť odvahu postaviť sa osudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.43,Rena,,0,0,0,,Napokon, si jedna z nás!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:15.13,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Poďme.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.54,Hanyuu,,0,0,0,,Ja som...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:18.30,Rena,,0,0,0,,Poďme všetci spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:28.41,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,Poďme spolu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:30.72,Rika (starsia),,0,0,0,,do nášho nového sveta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dvetisíc!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To je dvetisíc ľudí!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Predovšetkým musíme pokárať pánov z Tokia za to, že prišli s tak absurdnou myšlienkou a toto všetko spôsobili.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako som už vysvetlil, Hinamizawský Syndróm je extrémne nebezpečné ochorenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ak sa rozšíri, počet obetí vysoko prekročí dvetisíc ľudí.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Preto je nutné prijať zodpovedajúce rozhodnutia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Udržíte počet obetí na minime, áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To Vám môžem prisľúbiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Začnite so sterilizáciou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Prvý oddiel centrále.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sterilizácia budovy lesnej správy dokončená.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Museli sme zastreliť štyroch utečencov.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Druhý oddiel centrále.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Približne desať ľudí uteká smerom do hôr.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Prenasledujeme ich.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bez kliatby nieje žiaden boh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bez kliatby nieje žiaden strach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A bez strachu nieje žiadna úcta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Zosadila som boha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A ja som nový Oyashiro-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:25.00,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}anata no nakigara ni tsuchi wo kakeru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:25.00,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Zakrývam tvoje mŕtve telo zemou,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:32.98,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}sore ga kinjirareteita toshitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:32.98,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}aj keď viem že je to zakázané.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:41.89,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}junsui na manazashi no kairaku ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:41.89,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Spomínam na nádej ktorú som vídavala
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:49.71,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}kakushikirenai yuuwaku ga atta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:49.71,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}v tvojich čistých, šťastných očiach.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:58.55,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}doushite tsumi ga aru no darou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:58.55,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Prečo existujú hriechy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:05.52,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}doushite batsu ga aru no darou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:05.52,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Prečo existujú tresty?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:14.92,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}hori no saki wa amari ni mo shiroku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:14.92,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}To jasné svetlo na konci tunela
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:22.87,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}mugen ni tsuzuku yami wo sasotta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:22.87,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ťa pozvalo do nekonečnej tmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:31.12,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}nani mo kamo ga azayaka ni miete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:31.12,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Ale ja už už vidím všetko jasne.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:40.32,Karaoke_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}sugu ni kieteshimau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:40.32,Karaoke_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I ono čoskoro zmizne.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:45.44,Rika,Rika,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to ask you something for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:46.72,Hanyuu,Hanyuu,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.72,0:23:50.11,Rika,Rika,0,0,0,,What's with your "au au"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:55.80,Hanyuu,Hanyuu,0,0,0,,Ah, that's me expressing a certain emotion as an imitative sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:24:02.00,Rika,Rika,0,0,0,,You mean, when things go bad for you, you let everyone around you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:08.44,Rika,,0,0,0,,"I'm in trouble", and act all cute while implying you don't want anyone prying any further? {i made this spilt not sure if its ok like this or not so check-campa}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.44,0:24:10.72,Hanyuu,Hanyuu,0,0,0,,Ha, auau...{（´･ω･｀）}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.72,0:24:13.19,Rika,Rika,0,0,0,,It looks like I hit the nail on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.19,0:24:17.24,Rika,Rika,0,0,0,,Next episode: Festival Music Chapter, Part 1: Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:22.09,Hanyuu,Hanyuu,0,0,0,,Hau! Au! That's not it! That's not it at all!
